{"type":"message","id":"b69c79c0","parentId":"3121e4a6","timestamp":"2026-06-13T19:01:11.161Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-06-14 03:01 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: 好的，接任务！先并行摸清所有 SOUL.md 的位置和当前 memory-core 配置。\n- Assistant: Let me do a broader search for all SOUL.md files and check the agent workspace directories:\n- Assistant: Good, now I see the structure. `~/.openclaw/agents/<name>/` has an `agent/` subdirectory. Let me check there for SOUL.md files.\n- Assistant: Let me do a thorough search across the entire openclaw structure:\n- Assistant: Good. I found main's SOUL.md at `~/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md`. Now let me check the other agent workspaces:\n- Assistant: So `~/workspace-agent-orchestrator/` itself has the orchestrator files. The sub-workspaces `workspace-tts/` etc. don't exist there. Let me search more broadly for all SOUL.md files across the system:\n- Assistant: Now I have a clear picture. Let me identify all 10 agent SOUL.md files and verify which ones exist:\n- Assistant: All 11 paths exist. Let me now verify which tts path is the primary one by checking both:\n- Assistant: Now I have a clear picture. Let me read the end of each SOUL.md to find the right insertion point, then execute both tasks in parallel. **Key findings:** - `~/.openclaw/workspace/workspace-tts/SOUL.md` = TK 选品大师 (the real tts agent) - `~/workspace-tts/SOUL.md` = defaul\n- Assistant: Now I have the full picture. Let me plan: **Task A**: Insert \"记忆铁律\" after the \"风格/section\" equivalent in each of 10 SOUL.md files. The files have very different structures: - **main**: Insert after \"## 气质\" section - **agent-orchestrator**: Insert after \"## 风格\" (before\n- Assistant: Now I have the content of the first 3. Let me read the remaining 7 in parallel, then execute all edits at once.\n- Assistant: Now I have all 10 SOUL.md files mapped. Let me execute all edits in parallel. Here are the insertion 